==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Americanism
<hw>A*mer"i*can*ism</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Attachment to the United States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A custom peculiar to the United States or to
America; an American characteristic or idea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A word or phrase peculiar to the United
States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Americanization</ent>⟦br⟧
